npx sequelize-cli db:migrate
npx sequelize-cli db:seed:all
That creates the tables and seeds the default courses.

üîÑ 4. Recap: Associations & Methods
User ‚Üí Address: one-to-one via UserId foreign key.

User ‚Üí Posts: one-to-many via UserId.

User ‚Üî Course: many-to-many via UserCourses with composite PK.
Sequelize will generate methods like user.addCourse(), user.getCourses(), user.setCourses() etc. 
